■  課程其他要求 (Other Requirements)Working with Oxford University Press, the English Language Center provides an online practice system.  Students are required to buy access codes along with the SENM textbooks, which gives them access to both a reading and writing program and a speaking and listening program.  This provides four skills practice for all students.  Students are required to spend at least one hour per week using the SENM Online Program.  Student login time is recorded and their exercises will be monitored.


