三、課程大綱 Syllabus (本課程大綱教師得依實際教學進度及學生學習情況進行調整)


■  課程目標 (Course Objectives)The objectives of the course are to maximize students opportunities to speak English in class, to listen to English spoken by people of various nationalitis, to use basic reading skills, and to maximize students use of written English for formal communication. 


■  主要參考書籍/資料 (Textbooks and References)
