四、課程內涵與學生核心能力之對應Correspondence Between CourseContents and Core Competency



                學生核心能力  Core Competency
1.運用英語文於日常生活中之能力。The ability to use English in daily life.。2.運用英語文進行邏輯思考、分析判斷、整合創新之能力。The ability to think independently, logically, analytically, synthetically, and creatively in English.。3.瞭解及增進個人學習英語文興趣與動機之能力。The ability to understand and enhance one’s own interest and motivtion in learning English.。4.運用英語文吸收及瞭解多元領域知識之能力。The ability to use English to acquire and understand knowledge of various disciplines.。5.運用各類英語文學習策略之能力。The ability to use various English language learning strategies.。6.運用各類資源學習英語文之能力。The ability to use various English language learning sources.。7.運用英語文探索及瞭解國際多元文化之能力。The ability to use English to explore and understand various cultures in the world.。8.運用英語文探索及瞭解自我人生意義之能力。The ability to use English to explore and understand the meaning of one’s own life.。 








學生核心能力 Core Competency


